<subSubSection pageId="263" pageNumber="264" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="263.[151,1437,1554,2013]" pageId="263" pageNumber="264">
REMARKS: 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[267,503,1807,1834]" pageId="263" pageNumber="264" pagination="63 - 112" refId="ref368107" refString="Rondani, C. (1848 b) Esame di varie specie d'insetti ditteri brasiliani. Studi Entomologici, 1 (1), 63 - 112, pl. IIIbis." type="journal article" year="1848">Rondani (1848b: 67)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1848" box="[627,927,1807,1833]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Phalacromya" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="263" pageNumber="264" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="submetallica">
<emphasis box="[627,927,1807,1833]" italics="true" pageId="263" pageNumber="264">Phalacromya submetallica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from just the female sex, without specifying the exact 
<taxonomicName box="[310,396,1843,1869]" family="Number" pageId="263" pageNumber="26" rank="family">number</taxonomicName>
of specimens, but giving a single measurement of length, from material collected in South America by V. Ghiliani. 
<bibRefCitation author="Costa, A." box="[473,661,1879,1905]" pageId="263" pageNumber="264" pagination="13 - 48" refId="ref348459" refString="Costa, A. (1866) Acquisti fatti durante l'anno 1863. Annuario del Museo Zoologico della Regia Universita di Napoli, 3, 13 - 48." type="journal article" year="1866">Costa (1866: 31)</bibRefCitation>
listed a single MZUN specimen numbered “605”. We also found 
<specimenCount pageId="263" pageNumber="264" type="generic" typeStatus="syntype">one syntype</specimenCount>
in this study. Although 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[555,789,1915,1942]" pageId="263" pageNumber="264" pagination="63 - 112" refId="ref368107" refString="Rondani, C. (1848 b) Esame di varie specie d'insetti ditteri brasiliani. Studi Entomologici, 1 (1), 63 - 112, pl. IIIbis." type="journal article" year="1848">Rondani (1848b: 63)</bibRefCitation>
only gave the type locality as “ 
<collectingCountry box="[1143,1229,1915,1941]" name="Brazil" pageId="263" pageNumber="264">Brasile</collectingCountry>
”, 
<bibRefCitation author="Papavero, N." pageId="263" pageNumber="264" refId="ref362581" refString="Papavero, N. (1973) Essays on the history of Neotropical dipterology, with special reference to collectors (1750 - 1905). Vol. 2. Museu de Zoologia, Universidade de Sao Paolo, Sao Paolo, pp. 217 - 446." type="book" year="1973">Papavero (1973: 343)</bibRefCitation>
gave a more accurate type locality based on a note in 
<bibRefCitation author="Spinola, M." box="[863,1030,1950,1977]" pageId="263" pageNumber="264" pagination="19 - 94" refId="ref374743" refString="Spinola, M. (1853) Compte rendu des hymenopteres inedits provenants du voyage entomologique de M. Ghiliani dans le Para en 1846. Memorie della Reale Accademia delle Scienze di Torino, Series 2, 13, 19 - 94." type="journal article" year="1853">Spinola (1853)</bibRefCitation>
that said all specimens collected by Ghiliani in 1846 were collected in Belem, Pará, 
<collectingCountry box="[739,811,1987,2013]" name="Brazil" pageId="263" pageNumber="264">Brazil</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
